  'komiksy' => 'Comics',
  'komiksy_descr' => 'It would seem that the mouse cursor is a trifle, but often it’s such details that can improve your mood, wake up in the gray morning or just give bright emotions. A collection of comic book cursors designed specifically for all superhero lovers. Here you can find absolutely all the Marvel Universe and DC Comics - from Iron Man to Thanos, Spider-Man and Hulk. The cursor style can be either in the form of a superhero, or in the form of his character. A cursor is not just a functional element; it is important in a professional sense. For example, if you recording a video from the screen, it will be better to see a bright, original picture, and it looks much more interesting. And of course - who would not want to use the glove of infinity in real life? Changing the mouse cursor is simple - just download the extension to your browser and add the cursor you like to your settings through it. You can choose a cursor according to your mood at least every day. Enough the gray days - become a superhero right now!',
