  'lol_surprise' => 'L.O.L. Surprise',
  'lol_surprise_descr' => 'LOL Surprise dolls fell in love with children and won their hearts from the first minutes. And this is not surprising, because such success is based on a mystery, the expectation of a miracle, a pleasant surprise, which delights not only kids, but also their parents. The secret of the gift is revealed to the child only after the final unpacking. In any case, LOL dolls are an attractive design, intrigue, a large number of amazing and realistic accessories and pleasant little things, as well as the highest quality of production and detailing of the toy.',
