  'miraculous' => 'Miraculous: Tales of Ladybug & Cat Noir',
  'miraculous_descr' => 'Miraculous: Tales of Ladybug and Cat Noir, better known as Miraculous Ladybug and Cat Noir, are adventures of superheroes from the cartoon about two classmates who, under masks, play the role of defenders of Paris from a villain who in each episode comes up with a new way to harm the city. Miraculous is made in France using CGI and animation. Miraculous is not only an animated series, but also a collection of comics released around the world. The series is very loved by the young audience.

The action takes place in Paris, where Marinette and Adrian are high school students in a modern school. They were given the role of becoming the chosen one in the fight against evil, saving their hometown. Their goal is to protect people from Akumas. These small creatures in the form of butterflies are able to inhabit a person and turn him into a villain.

