  'multfilmy' => 'Cartoons',
  'multfilmy_descr' => 'Inside every adult there is still a child who loves cartoons, and still dreams of becoming one of the heroes. We will help to make your dreams come true - use the new collection of cursors based on the most famous and favorite cartoons. Tom and Jerry, Buzz Lightyear and Shrek, Gravity Falls and even Pokemon - you can become what you want every day. Select the mouse cursor according to your mood. Who are you today? Reckless and cheerful minion who easily solves any problems or a strong and courageous Raphael, whose goal is not only to accomplish feats, but also to eat pizza? Maybe you are the almighty genie who holds an entire office under his command? In the collection there are heroes for everyone - from princesses to dragons - it remains only to decide who reflects todays mood. The cursor style is not just a bright picture. This is a reflection of individuality, self-expression and simply - fun, joy and positive for the whole day. Is it boring to work or too lazy to study? Has it become sad and is not happy? Change the cursor and the world will sparkle with new colors.',
