  'naruto_anime' => 'Naruto anime',
  'naruto_anime_descr' => 'On Naruto Uzumaki\'s birthday, a legendary demon, the Nine-Tailed Fox, attacked a village called Konoha. The Fourth Hokage, at the cost of his life, saved the village by sealing the demon in the newborn Naruto, unknowingly dooming him to a life of hatred from his fellow villagers.
Despite his lack of talent in many areas of ninjutsu, restlessness and snobbishness, Naruto has a dream to become Hokage, the strongest ninja in the village. Desiring the recognition he didn\'t get, he works hard and trains alongside his teammates Sasuke Uchiha and Sakura Haruno, as well as his mentor Kakashi Hatake. He and his partners will have to go through a lot on the way to their cherished dreams: battles, love, friendship, betrayal, thirst for power. A collection of Naruto anime cursors will help you navigate your own path!',
