  'prazdniki' => 'Holidays',
  'prazdniki_descr' => 'Like the holidays? But who does not like them - friends, gifts, again the same weekend. To make the wait for the holidays more pleasant, shorter and warmer, you can not only count the days on the calendar, but also set the corresponding icon as the mouse cursor. Let′s start with the New Year - we will choose a Christmas tree, a gift or Santa Claus, so that the holiday is bright and cheerful. Maybe the gingerbread man will be closer - funny, cute and always cheerful? With him certainly there will be no time to be sad and bored. We continue to celebrate with cupids and cheerful hearts, and there is not far to the Easter Bunny. Somewhere among the holidays, there will be a birthday, which will be even more pleasant to wait with balloons instead of the standard cursor arrow. And in Halloween, you can surprise colleagues and those around you with an unusual mouse cursor in the form of an ominous pumpkin or a ghost. A set of cursors for the holidays is an opportunity to brighten up the expectation, tune in advance for the upcoming fun and maintain an excellent mood not only on the eve of the celebration, but throughout the year.',
