  'spider-man' => 'Spider-Man',
  'spider-man_descr' => 'A collection of characters and heroes from the Spider-Man universe. Includes various versions of Spider-Man, allies, and unique styles from across comics, games, and animated series. Each design reflects the agility, courage, and visual identity that defines the Spider-Man world.',
