  'sports-cars' => 'Sports Cars',
  'sports-cars_descr' => 'Sports cars are high-performance vehicles designed for fast acceleration, sharp handling, and an exciting driving experience. From sleek coupes to agile roadsters, this category features some of the most iconic machines built for the thrill of the road or track. Ideal for enthusiasts who love speed, design, and power. 🏎️🔥',
