  'starwars' => 'Star Wars',
  'starwars_descr' => 'Dive into the galaxy far, far away with this collection featuring legendary heroes, powerful Sith lords, droids, rebels, and more. From Jedi Knights to stormtroopers, each icon brings the spirit of Star Wars to life in cursor form. Perfect for fans of every trilogy. 🌌',
