  'stil_i_krasota' => 'Fashion and style',
  'stil_i_krasota_descr' => 'In the new collection of cursors, we have collected a wide variety of subjects that cause us pleasant emotions and uplift. This set of cursors is called “Style and Beauty”, because it is your favorite things that determine our everyday life, give joy and motivate us to do important things, awaken the desire for improvement. Are you keen on space and dream of going to other planets? Choose a NASA cursor or a plate of aliens - get closer to your dream. If you can not imagine life without music or are an inveterate rocker, then the cursor in the style of an electric guitar is for you. The brush, ruler and compass cursor has been specially developed for engineers - such images will help turn boring calculations and drawings into original solutions. A magic wand and sneakers, a skateboard and lipstick, the sun and chemical cones - choose what suits your lifestyle, your desires and aspirations - and ordinary tasks will become more interesting, and workdays will be painted in new, bright colors.',
