  'test_zone' => 'TESTING AREA',
  'text_1' => 'You do not want to be like everyone else? Or just love everything unusual? Want to be a part of your favorite game hero or cartoon character? Then you have come to the right address. Here you will find bright, unusual sets of cursors that can replace the familiar and already pretty boring white arrow. The mouse cursor accompanies us all day in work and study, so it should give a great mood and set up for positive.',
  'text_2' => 'Here you will find cursors for gamers and movie lovers, beautiful cursors based on your favorite cartoons and sports motives for the most active people. Do you like comics or can\'t imagine a single day without funny memes? Do you adore animals or dream of visiting all countries of the world? Everything is simple - we have a suitable cursor image for you too. You can also select images depending on what you are working with. For example, a black cursor will be much more convenient than white when working with documents or drawings, and a hand cursor will be more convenient if you have to work with small graphic elements. Choose your favorite image, adjust its size directly in the extension - and use it with pleasure, every day starting with a positive note!',
